Dorsal, lateral and front view of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3C4D21FFB7FFA2FD7BF8C5DC50F806" baseAuthorityName="Schedl" baseAuthorityYear="1961" box="[688,1041,1899,1923]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Pseudomicracis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="334" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="madagascariensis">
