Dorsal, lateral and front view of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3C4D21FFB4FFA1FD7AF836DB90F835" authorityName="Jordal" authorityYear="2022" box="[689,977,1944,1968]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Pseudomicracis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="335" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vitrioculata">
